61 void callbackOdometry(const nav_msgs::Odometry::ConstPtr& odometry)
62 {
63  poseOdom[0] = odometry -> pose.pose.position.x;
64  poseOdom[1] = odometry -> pose.pose.position.y;
65 
66  Quaternion orientationQ;
67  orientationQ.x = odometry -> pose.pose.orientation.x;
68  orientationQ.y = odometry -> pose.pose.orientation.y;
69  orientationQ.z = odometry -> pose.pose.orientation.z;
70  orientationQ.w = odometry -> pose.pose.orientation.w;
71 
72  EulerAngles orientationE;
73  orientationE = ToEulerAngles(orientationQ);
74  poseOdom[2] = (orientationE.yaw*180.0)/PI;
75 
76  initialOdom = true;
77 }

84 void callbackGT(const gazebo_msgs::ModelStates::ConstPtr& GT)
85 {
86  poseGT[0] = GT->pose[2].position.x;
87  poseGT[1] = GT->pose[2].position.y;
88 
89  Quaternion orientationQ;

91  orientationQ.y = GT->pose[2].orientation.y;
92  orientationQ.z = GT->pose[2].orientation.z;
93  orientationQ.w = GT->pose[2].orientation.w;
94 
95  EulerAngles orientationE;

154  drivePub = nh.advertise<geometry_msgs::Twist>("/cmd_vel", 100);

156  // classes for navigation and DFS algorithm

163  // set pointer to GT or odom

166  DFS.currentPose = poseGT;
167  navigation.currentPose = poseGT;
168  }
169  else if(argument == "odom")
170  {
171  DFS.currentPose = poseOdom;
172  navigation.currentPose = poseOdom;
173  }
174 
175  // startup and waiting for initial sensor data
176  while(ros::ok())
177  {
178  if(initialLidar && initialGT && initialOdom)
179  {
180  cout << "STARTUP complete" << endl;
181  initialSeconds = currentSeconds;
182 
183  break;
184  }
185 
186  ros::spinOnce();
187  }
188  auto start = std::chrono::high_resolution_clock::now();
189 
190  // loop solving the maze
191  while(ros::ok())
192  {
193  // if new position is reached calculate the next movement
194  if(positionReached){
195  positionReached = false;
196  if(DFS.handleNode()){
197  auto finish = std::chrono::high_resolution_clock::now();
198  std::chrono::duration<double> durationReal = finish - start;
199  CSV.writeSuccess(DFS.getNodeNumber(), (currentSeconds-initialSeconds), durationReal);
200  break;
201  }
202  }
203 
204  // navigate to next movement
205  if(navigation.moveTo(nextPosition))
206  positionReached = true;
207  ros::spinOnce();
208  }
209  //system("~jakob/SOA_ws/src/soa_pkg/kill.bash");
210 
211 return 0;
212 }
